                    <div class="exc-description">
                        <p><span style="font-weight: 400;">When we think about a strong athletic physique; few body parts grab our attention like shredded arms.</span></p><p><span style="font-weight: 400;">Whether you are wearing a singlet or sleeves, strong, muscular arms make a lasting first impression.Â </span></p><p><span style="font-weight: 400;">No exercise builds incredible arms like the barbell reverse curl, a forearm-targeting, bicep-building exercise that will enhance your physique.</span></p><p><span style="font-weight: 400;">Today, we will discuss everything you need to know about the barbell reverse curl. Covering how to perform the exercise, primary and secondary target muscles, and more. </span></p>                    </div>
